</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/Flc4OZ94U7k" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/30/facebook-watch-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=facebook-watch-2</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>31 年前全新紅白機、大哥大被掘出   NTT 時間囊藏當年「尖端科技」</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/Iud_TMbXL_g/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 30 Oct 2021 04:05:03 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[NTT]]></category><category><![CDATA[大哥大]]></category><category><![CDATA[時間囊]]></category><category><![CDATA[紅白機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1068721</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>曾經風靡全城的大哥大、紅白機隨時日變遷變得不再普及，亦漸漸被遺忘和取代。近日日本電信電話 NTT 舉行開封儀式 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>曾經風靡全城的大哥大、紅白機隨時日變遷變得不再普及，亦漸漸被遺忘和取代。近日日本電信電話 NTT 舉行開封儀式，將 1990 年埋下的時間囊挖起，在經歷 31 年的時間囊中，驚現大哥大及紅白機等當年的科技產品。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.44.50.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068769" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.44.50-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.44.50-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.44.50-1280x716.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.44.50-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.44.50-1536x859.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.44.50-2048x1145.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.44.50.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.19.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.19-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.19-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.19-1280x716.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.19-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.19-1536x859.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.19-2048x1145.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.19.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>於 1990 年，正值 NTT 在日本設立首個電話接線所的 100 周年，因此 NTT 當年將具代表性的時代產物放到時間囊中。按計劃該時間囊只會埋藏 30 年，但上年受到疫情的影響，便將開封儀式順延至今年，並於石川縣金澤市的「西日本北陸支店」舉行開封儀式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.34.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.34-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.34-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.34-1280x716.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.34-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.34-1536x859.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.34-2048x1145.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.34.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.44.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.44-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.44-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.44-1280x716.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.44-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.44-1536x859.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.44-2048x1145.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.44.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.50.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068773" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.50-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.50-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.50-1280x716.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.50-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.50-1536x859.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.50-2048x1145.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.45.50.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.46.00.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.46.00-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.46.00-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.46.00-1280x716.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.46.00-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.46.00-1536x859.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.46.00-2048x1145.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.46.00.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>歷時 31 年的時間囊當中包括各式各樣令人懷念的產品，例如當時的報紙、書籍和簽滿員工名字的布匹。此外，更不少得當年的科技產品，例如座檯電話、包裝完好無缺的全新紅白機、已絕版的經典遊戲及重達 900g 的首支日產「大哥大」電話。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.50.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068776" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.50-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.50-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.50-1280x716.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.50-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.50-1536x859.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.50-2048x1145.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.50.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.38.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1068775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.38-694x388.png" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.38-694x388.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.38-1280x716.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.38-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.38-1536x859.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.38-2048x1145.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-29-下午 7.50.38.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>有當年的員工到場見證開封的一刻，而該分店的店長更感嘆時代發展迅速。除此之外，開封儀式吸引了不少日本網民熱烈討論，認為它們具歷史價值，希望當局能妥善保存。</p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/9ec80b188dd9e4437b847bc1f85481116f11bacd">Yahoo! JAPAN</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
